if not databank then
    system.print("ERROR: No databank connected!")
    unit.exit()
    return
end

local keys = databank.getKeyList()
system.print("=== HASKEY TEST ===")
system.print("Total keys: " .. #keys)
system.print("")

system.print("First 10 keys:")
for i = 1, math.min(10, #keys) do
    system.print("  [" .. i .. "] " .. keys[i])
end
system.print("")

local testKeys = {"hematite", "bauxite", "coal", "quartz", "hematite.c", "bauxite.c", "coal.c", "quartz.c"}
system.print("Testing hasKey():")
for _, key in ipairs(testKeys) do
    local result = databank.hasKey(key)
    system.print("  hasKey('" .. key .. "') = " .. tostring(result))
    if result == 1 then
        system.print("    Value type: " .. type(databank.getStringValue(key)))
    end
end

unit.exit()
